===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''thimble'''
# a [[pitted]] [[metal]] [[cap]] for the [[finger]]s, that is used in [[sewing]] to [[push]] the [[needle]]
# a similarly shaped [[socket]] in [[machinery]]
# a [[thimbleful]] of something
#{{nautical}} any of various metal [[ring]]s used in a ship's [[rigging]]

